{"tid":917911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣最憎人喺書店做嘅嘢","createTime":"2018-11-26T19:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:01:29.000Z","uid":99039,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"957a150109491f33b08a7a2fe92189b33f4f4312","tid":917911,"uid":99039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:13:24.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n話說今日去咗書店買書<br />\n宜家開嚟睇先發現<br />\n本書爛咗少少<br />\n入面送嘅書簽同優惠券都冇咗<br />\n點解我會知有得送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為同一系列嘅書我買咗3本<br />\n另外嗰2本都有<br />\n其實張優惠券我都可以由得佢<br />\n但張書簽我真係想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗有買開書嘅人都明<br />\n買得一系列都係想齊齊整整啫<br />\n你宜家咁<br />\n啫係想點<br />\n<br />\n好心啲人啦<br />\n你唔買書返屋企睇都算<br />\n點解仲要偷嘢<br />\n真心覺得連呢啲嘢都偷嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住聽日拎返去書局睇吓換唔換到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總結：<br />\n以後買書前要檢查清楚<br />\n最好係買啲有膠膜包實晒嘅書"},{"pid":"63165027d50f73e01305e6b8c295d5e386286144","tid":917911,"uid":136186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:14:24.000Z","msg":"買書"},{"pid":"3e7789b880d29b8f3cc151d11c0645c1d97066a9","tid":917911,"uid":99039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63165027d50f73e01305e6b8c295d5e386286144","tid":917911,"uid":136186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:14:24.000Z","msg":"買書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:17:03.000Z","msg":"咁你咪好憎我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8447b1e4d7cdf9a8bb1cac0d2e9935f06e7b5a4","tid":917911,"uid":167326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"放屁 但我成日入書店就想放"},{"pid":"5dd73cfd80691e5d386046a0f347b1266b6103db","tid":917911,"uid":41368,"